------------------------------------------------

New in this release

   * a11y fixes (Mengjie Yu)
   * cursor movement fixes
   * color changes notification fix (Mengjie Yu)
   * stress test suite
   * fixed table cells parsing
   * fixed deleting around tables
   * updated translations (Abel Cheung)

