   * beginning of rtl support - HTML tags
   * i18n fixes - use glib's i18n instead of deprecated libgnome i18n (Mariano Suarez-Alvarez)
   * fixed crash in aligned images drawing
   * use more GIT icons
   * fixed two memory leaks

